/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUijYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=35cca993\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 宣傳</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUijYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=c2cc4456\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">三罷 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://T.me/hkgeneralstrike9293\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FT.me%2Fhkgeneralstrike9293&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUijYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=931713c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">T.me/hkgeneralstrike9293</a></span>"},{"pid":"e09ef5a2cd74bdea771fd5237e7965a834152f9d","tid":1518733,"uid":260035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T10:34:29.000Z","msg":"香港科學園一間公司剛剛被美國制裁，它叫「綠色工業（香港）有限公司」，涉嫌向伊朗非法轉運價值數千萬美元的美國原產技術和電子零件，以研發大規模殺傷性武器&mdash;&mdash;還記得我建議大家把林鄭和魯哈尼的假人綁在一起嗎？<br />\n<br />\n「我們建議美國出口商及其海外子公司審查位於香港的客戶，以確保採購供應商的產品和技術具有合法性。任何引起懷疑技術轉移的交易都應向美國執法官員報告。」美方根本暗示香港信不過。<br />\n<br />\n這個年頭，凡冠名綠色、智能的通常都不是好東西，李小琳在香港開一間「香港綠色健康發展有限公司」，就是借搞醫療之名在海南圈地的。這間綠色工業也用同一手段，掩藏它與伊朗和俄羅斯的勾當，非法轉口技術和零件&mdash;&mdash;香港，其實一直都是國際社會銷贓的集散地。<br />\n<br />\n看，美方連它在觀塘和灣仔有架部都查得一清二楚：<br />\n<br />\n2/F, Green 18, Phase 2, Hong Kong Science Park, Pak Shek Kok, NT, Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\nFlat A10, 8/F, Hung Fuk Factory Building, 60 Hung To Road, Kwun Tong, Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\nUnit D, 16/F, One Capital Place, 18 Luard Road, Wan Chai, Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\n這只是制裁港共的第一着。下一步，將會劍指金融機構，美國財政部警告金融機構萬勿促進伊朗的擴張活動，言下之意是他們已掌握相當的證據，知道香港的銀行提供支持恐怖主義的資金。大家只要google一下「滙豐+墨西哥毒販」，就會明白那案底有幾花。而指證孟晚舟與伊朗做生意的，也是滙豐。<br />\n<br />\n由林鄭宣佈香港不會遵守美國的伊朗出口石油禁令那天起，我就知道她遲早會死在這個關節之上。如果大家在示威時懂得在文宣上玩起伊朗與香港合污的元素，隨時推波助瀾，促使特朗普在9月尾（如果成事的話）見魯哈尼期間把香港問題放在美伊的談判桌上。<br />\n<br />\n香港的外交權，現在不在中共手上，也不在林鄭手上&mdash;&mdash;它在民間的大家手上啊！<br />\n<br />\n//Iran traded 94,242 tons of non-oil commodities worth $344.08 million with Hong Kong during the last Iranian year (ended March 20, 2019) to register a 32.51% and 29.88% decline in tonnage and value respectively compared with the year before, latest data released by the Islamic Republic of Iran Customs Administration show. Iran&rsquo;s exports to Hong Kong stood at 73,289 million tons worth $202.57 million, down 11.36% and 47.3% in tonnage and value respectively year-on-year. //<br />\n<br />\n作者<br />\n<br />\n#香港涉幫伊朗製核彈"},{"pid":"e0d39efd6690165f951d3340ffdf42f910732068","tid":1518733,"uid":277084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T10:37:38.000Z","msg":"p牌push唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dced18cbc1414384a423e6fb12d81878fd140f8","tid":1518733,"uid":5220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T10:38:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/2/23/Bundesarchiv_B_145_Bild-F088809-0038%2C_Berlin%2C_East_Side_Gallery.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F2%2F23%2FBundesarchiv_B_145_Bild-F088809-0038%252C_Berlin%252C_East_Side_Gallery.jpg&h=b61a7712&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMy God, Help Me to Survive this Deadly Love<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54e6a6a3b86cb271f892b844f8cfefd67b9123d0","tid":1518733,"uid":260035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T10:39:14.000Z","msg":"幫推 我p仔推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bc7ceb80644ff8550a1a876e169807002037a6a","tid":1518733,"uid":34798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T11:02:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"55eaab876e29ca67b41fafba8b30ee93a433baf6","tid":1518733,"uid":12360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T11:04:32.000Z","msg":"呢個超核彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac2e51255855940ac0847487d41c9d783a839ad5","tid":1518733,"uid":5220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T11:33:20.000Z","msg":"建議畫埋下半身<br />\n柒婆塞份寫住US Tech嘅文件去魯哈尼個衫袋度"},{"pid":"2899311c23924af2e9cee6e55956a4e8a635cec5","tid":1518733,"uid":12360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T12:17:40.000Z","msg":"呢個要推"},{"pid":"6936ad1353b2f83fb393d0357ea48db7094a7b03","tid":1518733,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T12:20:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c8a426e3bba8a1a00eb291ff6ba59b7c2c1eba6","tid":1518733,"uid":236011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T12:31:50.000Z","msg":"好嘔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f667ae977ec6b2e5d7d9148c823e6a8abe8d00e","tid":1518733,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T14:43:21.000Z","msg":"推"}]}